e6 $2 {(Black has the weak squares b6 and c7; after the e6 move all the dark
squares became weak.)} ({it's was better to play a normal development move} 
12... Be6 {Now} 13. Bc7 {doesn't do much} Qd7) 13. Bc7 Qe7 (13... Qd7 14. Na4 {
and Nb6}) 14. a3 {(We should mainly attack opponent's weaknesses. They are the
easiest targets for our attack. Now white is going to transfer the knight to
